    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that defines the 'mint' standard. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and the interior retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. From the pristine undercarriage to the original, unmarked alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48900.0,
